data.description: INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY WITH IMMEDIATE EQUITY AFTER SOME TLC! This is one of the largest homes for sale currently in Sonoma Ranch! Amazing two-story home w/3,172 sq ft with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a huge game room! This home features a formal dining area, study, kitchen with eat-dining that opens to the family room. There is a 2 car attached garage and a fully fenced back yard. The rooms are spacious and the master bedroom comes equipped with a full master bath that has his/her sinks, tub with separate stand up shower, and walk-in closet. Enjoy the community pool, parks and clubhouse (available to rent for private parties by homeowners). Prime location with easy access to I-10, beltway 8 and Hwy 90. 20 minutes from Downtown Houston. Conveniently located near shopping, groceries, restaurants, and entertainment! Schedule your tour today!
